#1 Instalar dotnet  .NET SDK (ej: .NET 7 o 8) 
https://dotnet.microsoft.com/en-us/download

#2 Install SQL Server With Docker#
docker run -e "ACCEPT_EULA=Y" -e "SA_PASSWORD=TuPasswordFuerte123" -p 1433:1433 --name sqlserver -d mcr.microsoft.com/mssql/server:2019-latest

#3 INstalar SQL Server Managment
https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/ssms/download-sql-server-management-studio-ssms